blogs.author: Zem
blogs.description: Best Char Siu ramen in Tokyo. The meat is satisfactory and huge.
Compared with other ramen, this one boasts mild flavor. If one has little appetite for strong flavor; then this is the place to go.
blogs.author: Zem

blogs.ramenShopName: 山下公園 ラーメン
blogs.description: I always love ramen. This place is definitely for egg lovers cuz they serve smoked dove eggs with a tasty ajitsuke tamago. They also have potstickers. Dun forget to have a ramen when you visit Taichung.
